          <h1>Clarence Gono</h1>
          
          <p>
            Real estate web developer and SEO specialist building ranked websites for luxury agents. I work remotely from the Philippines for clients across the US, focused on Sierra Interactive and Luxury Presence platforms.
          </p>

          <p>
            The core problem: most real estate sites don't rank and don't convert. I fix that by combining solid technical SEO, conversion-focused design, and platform expertise.
          </p>

          <div class="credentials">
            <p><strong>Upwork:</strong> Top Rated Plus, 100% Job Success, 5.0 rating</p>
            <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> Sierra Interactive, Luxury Presence, custom Astro builds</p>
            <p><strong>Also:</strong> Web & SEO VA for LUXURYSOCALREALTY, La Jolla</p>
          </div>

          <p>
            I write about real estate SEO, generative engine optimization, and platform-specific strategies on the blog.
