        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="services">
        <h2>What I do</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>SEO & Ranking</h3>
            <p>Build and optimize real estate sites for search visibility. Schema, technical SEO, content strategy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Web Development</h3>
            <p>Custom website build on Sierra Interactive or Luxury Presence. Fast, clean, conversion-ready.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>Platform Expertise</h3>
            <p>Deep knowledge of Sierra Interactive and Luxury Presence. I know the quirks and how to work around them.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <h3>AI Visibility</h3>
            <p>Get agents named when buyers ask ChatGPT or Perplexity. Structured data and content optimization for generative engines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <h2>Let's talk</h2>
        <p>Got a site that needs ranking? Or just exploring options?</p>
        <p>
          Email me at <a href="mailto:clarencearongono133@gmail.com" class="contact-link">clarencearongono133@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Clarence Gono. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
